  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Synthetic Human Secretin-Enhanced MRCP in Subjects With Abnormalities of the Pancreas</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase III Study to Demonstrate the Efficacy and Safety of RG1068 (Synthetic Human Secretin)- Enhanced Magnetic Resonance Cholangiopancreatography (MRCP) in the Evaluation of Subjects With a History of Acute or Acute Recurrent Pancreatitis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
